\f0 : What impacts Car Price?\
\
  This is a case study for Practical Application 11.1.\
  My client is a used cars dealership. I analyzed a large dataset of over 400,000 used cars details, to come up with a data prepared for a linear \
  Regression model - a multiple regression, as there are many features.\
\
\
 - Overview file: PA_11_1_Overview.ipynb (attached in this repository). Contains conclusions and recommendations to the client.\
\
